summary: A house is added in the sky of Solitude.
descriptionHtml:
----------------
Sky Boat House (Ver 1.0)
----------------

A house is added in the sky of Solitude.

[color=red][b]Please be sure to back up your save file. [/b][/color]


---
Author : hdela


---
This mod was built with Skyrim US Ver 1.5.24.0


---
Installation : Unzip the file, and overwrite Skyrim Data folder. Or drop the esp into your Skyrim Data directory.


---
[color=skyblue][b]Ver 1.0[/b][/color] : Base MOD - WIP-B

There is no Navmesh on top of the Boat House.
Added the boat to the scenic location .

[color=lightblue][b]WIP-B[/b][/color] : Non navmesh version

There is no Navmesh on top of the Boat House.
Follower will stay in the Main Room (Interior space).
It is a version of the more stable operation. 

[color=lightblue][b]WIP[/b][/color] : First MOD

Double bed x3
No respawn container x21
Disply case x6

Alchemy Workbench
Enchanting Workbench
Smelter Marker
BlackSmith Forge
Armor Workbench 
Blacksmith Sharpening Wheel
Tanning Rack Marker
Cooking Pot


---
Enjoy!

by hdela
